    "body": "\nThere were multiple times when we wanted to use graph diagrams using mermaid.js, so we put together a real- time drawing method and created a tool to perform real- time drawing.\n\n## introduction\n\n```bash\n$ npm i mermaid\n$ npm i --save-dev @types/mermaid\n```\n\n## Drawing\n\n-  component.html\n\n```html\n<div class=\"mermaid\">\nsequenceDiagram\n\tAlice ->> Bob: hello\n</div>\n```\n\n-  component.ts\n\n```ts\nimport mermaid from 'mermaid'\n\nmermaid.initialize({ startOnLoad: true })\n```\n\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29157528/169693934-b1677536-7738-4ded-a905-da1a7c0edf09.png)\n\n\n## Make it draw again where it has already been drawn\n\n-  component.html\n\n```html\n<div class=\"mermaid\" #mermaid id=\"mermaid\">\nsequenceDiagram\n\tAlice ->> Bob: hello\n</div>\n```\n\n-  component.ts\n\n```ts\nimport mermaid from 'mermaid'\n\n@ViewChild('mermaid') mermaidDiv!: ElementRef<HTMLDivElement>;\n\n// mermaidが既に描画されている場合data-processed属性が付与されているため削除\nmermaidDiv.nativeElement.removeAttribute('data-processed');\n// 描画するテキストをinnerHTMLとして入力(innerTextの場合改行がbrタグになってしまうのでinnerHTMLの必要があります。)\nmermaidDiv.nativeElement.innerHTML = txt;\n// 初期化(描画)処理\nmermaid.init('#mermaid');\n```\n\n## End\n\nBased on the above implementation, we have created a page that renders mermaid.js in real time and facilitates description.\n\n[Mermaid Live Editor](https://portal.kemu.site/tools/mermaid/)",
